{"tid":1682250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［幫推］想成功三罷嘅入嚟傾下，唔想再失去前線手足","createTime":"2019-10-30T02:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T03:23:30.000Z","uid":81732,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0e543adc7d8c72b0dafc2838ce6a0a4193f5859a","tid":1682250,"uid":81732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"有無諗過點解香港一直都搞唔起三罷？<br />\n<br />\n罷學，問題應該唔大，有各大專學生會同中學關注組統籌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷巿，罷到工個巿自然收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">所以問題喺罷工到</span><br />\n<br />\n外國罷工嘅其中一個重要原素係工會，呢樣都係香港欠奉嘅野，好多人驚得自己一個罷其他人唔跟會被炒收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但問題又嚟啦，好多手足成日話要拆大台，咁工會又算唔算係大台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為此，我有個諗法，之前有其他巴打提過，就係分返唔同行業各自成立自己嘅公會，但唔需要一個大公會去統一，改為成堆工會主席坐低傾罷工安排，再向下傳達行動內容，咁工會會員喺會內見到夠多人跟機自然會突破心理關口，仲可以利用羊群心理拉埋啲1516嘅人一齊join<br />\n<br />\n工會嘅平台，可以係tg group, fb group, apps乜都得，但更重要嘅係工會框架本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拋磚引玉，歡迎各路巴絲提供更好嘅方案</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民三罷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">實現真正嘅</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"58dec99c3de202767615ad46910b7376780dfb30","tid":1682250,"uid":81732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"73e5124537fd31ee64c95864863db8b846060813","tid":1682250,"uid":81732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:42:01.000Z","msg":"大罷工=和理非核武"},{"pid":"c57350bd0a25ff6213fcf57d89d6c390bf5c550a","tid":1682250,"uid":81732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2774efb98657f9fcdf532d501e8bcb85823c3215","tid":1682250,"uid":213893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:44:38.000Z","msg":"之前三罷有人搞過行業tg group<br />\n唔work<br />\n主要真係太分散根本無得同公司deal <br />\n炒嘅炒照肺嘅照肺"},{"pid":"4e298a84a5ac45343c9ef51c1796957b1b712d53","tid":1682250,"uid":81732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df8e55690110525f2fdb0bdc340c2c1095e97d18","tid":1682250,"uid":270337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"幫推1"},{"pid":"f8bb11bad0e3f4824e4e169281be29ee1f27ad7e","tid":1682250,"uid":23104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ba7691b61c6fcb2ed09ae5577c93ed18b384ea","tid":1682250,"uid":270337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:45:47.000Z","msg":"幫推2"},{"pid":"062331021aff40e2b012c03ff787b04a7a89b80b","tid":1682250,"uid":270337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"幫推3"},{"pid":"ef5c95a73a976d2e7a15021b6dc51449fa88511f","tid":1682250,"uid":270337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"幫推4"},{"pid":"ff10c7c4814ca0f81dc028713eb5371b05938a76","tid":1682250,"uid":270337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:46:39.000Z","msg":"幫推5"},{"pid":"435e0262d098888bd7c36c78d6cd04a7b062efcb","tid":1682250,"uid":270337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"幫推6"},{"pid":"6068dd4cfbc3e63051f02769e9a918315391e0dc","tid":1682250,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:50:08.000Z","msg":"香港嚟講<br />\n我認為三罷需要至少一個月前籌備（香港人要請假呀）<br />\n而且時段以2-3日為目標（香港人請唔到咁多假呀）<br />\n老中青反而易話為啲<br />\n但中小學想參與難度會高（淨喺藍絲紅底屋企都咪使指意唔返學呀）<br />\n所以日期應該定喺假日後（方便各區手足配合凌晨起癱瘓各地交通）<br />\n宣傳必須持續進行<br />\n提前咁耐籌備亦可以比老闆家長少一個籍口話影響乜影響物（比各大公司例如四大提出彈性處理）"},{"pid":"2e8df074c2c04dab78295955ae902193246bfb9f","tid":1682250,"uid":270337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2774efb98657f9fcdf532d501e8bcb85823c3215","tid":1682250,"uid":213893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:44:38.000Z","msg":"之前三罷有人搞過行業tg group<br />\n唔work<br />\n主要真係太分散根本無得同公司deal <br />\n炒嘅炒照肺嘅照肺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:50:20.000Z","msg":"點解要同公司deal?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n太分散我都認同，所以點樣組織到先係最大問題，靠我地後生搞好易就變左圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5560cdc3067c5ca917a543abe391118939484431","tid":1682250,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:53:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc123e29848c6f051de60f8213025376ecd18fd6","tid":1682250,"uid":213893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e8df074c2c04dab78295955ae902193246bfb9f","tid":1682250,"uid":270337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2774efb98657f9fcdf532d501e8bcb85823c3215","tid":1682250,"uid":213893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:44:38.000Z","msg":"之前三罷有人搞過行業tg group<br />\n唔work<br />\n主要真係太分散根本無得同公司deal <br />\n炒嘅炒照肺嘅照肺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T02:50:20.000Z","msg":"點解要同公司deal?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n太分散我都認同，所以點樣組織到先係最大問題，靠我地後生搞好易就變左圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr